## Example C++ Program
```cpp
#include <iostream>

int main() {
    // Declare a variable
    int x = 5;

    // Print the value of x
    std::cout << "The value of x is: " << x << std::endl;

    // Use a control structure (if-else statement)
    if (x > 10) {
        std::cout << "x is greater than 10" << std::endl;
    } else {
        std::cout << "x is less than or equal to 10" << std::endl;
